summary: *****GAME OF THRONES SPOILERS, KINDA***** Hey, so a lot of people are trying to speculate what weapon Arya special ordered, but...
body:
*****GAME OF THRONES SPOILERS, KINDA*****

Hey, so a lot of people are trying to speculate what weapon Arya special ordered, but I’m pretty sure we already see it in the trailer? No one’s pointed it out that I’ve seen (everyone keeps saying its the dagger she has in the trailer).

In the season trailer, she’s shown twirling around a spear. Could be wrong, I guess, but I think Needle has been shown to work well at poking holes, not rending and killing in great battles, so she definitely needs something stronger, but that still leans into the agile fighting style she uses.

idk I just had to say something. I’m on the third video I’ve watched where guys are like “we just don’t know what she could possibly be getting made! Maybe a small dagger!” I could be wrong, of course, but I’m not sure why else Arya would be swinging a pole around, when the major battle that will probably happen is between the living and the dead.
